  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header>
        <h1>Developer Davis</h1>
        <nav>
          <a href="#contacts" class="contact">Contact me</a>
          <a
            href="https://developerdavis.netlify.app"
            target="_blank"
            class="contact"
            >My projects</a
          >
        </nav>
      </header>
      <aside>
        <section class="aside-stuff">
          <h2>Keep time</h2>
          <p>
            This is a gift that I received from a friend #Klein_Clive. Thanks
            bro!
          </p>
          <div class="clock">
            <div class="hour-hand"></div>
            <div class="minute-hand"></div>
            <div class="second-hand"></div>
            <div class="center-circle"></div>
          </div>
          <p>
            Sorry this is limited to large screens But you can turn on desktop
            mode in you mobile device to see it.
          </p>
        </section>
      </aside>
      <main>
        <div class="personal">
          <p>Hey I'm Davis, a fullstack developer</p>
          <div class="stacks">
            <h2>My stacks</h2>
            <ul>
              <li>MERN</li>
              <li>PHP-Mysql</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <h2>Technologies</h2>
          <ol class="techs">
            <li>
              <h3>Frontend</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>HTML</li>
                <li>JavaScript</li>
                <li>CSS</li>
                <li>React</li>
                <li>jQuery</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h3>Backend</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Node.js</li>
                <li>express js</li>
                <li>ejs</li>
                <li>Mongoose</li>
                <li>PHP</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h3>Databases</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>MongoDB</li>
                <li>MySQL</li>
                <li>Firebase</li>
              </ul>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>
        <section class="css-stuff">
          <h2>How about a little bit of CSS?</h2>
          <p>In here we gonna have some pics of me and the boys...</p>
          <div class="css-projects">
            <div class="css-project">
              <h3>You could build a lil' gallery you know</h3>
              <p>Where pics move én move én....</p>
              <div class="album">
                <img src="images/images(1).jfif" alt="one" />
                <img src="images/images(2).jfif" alt="two" />
                <img src="images/images(3).jfif" alt="three" />
                <img src="images/images(4).jfif" alt="four" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="css-project">
              <h3>You could make it interactive too</h3>
              <p>Have a closer look at each pic by hovering or clicking</p>
              <div class="pie">
                <img src="images/images(1).jfif" alt="one" />
                <img src="images/images(2).jfif" alt="two" />
                <img src="images/images(3).jfif" alt="three" />
                <img src="images/images(4).jfif" alt="four" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="css-project">
              <h3>
                You could do a sneak peek too... You know.. not the entire thing
              </h3>
              <p>Again hover or click what you wanna see</p>
              <div class="box">
                <img src="images/images(1).jfif" alt="one" />
                <img src="images/images(3).jfif" alt="two" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        <div class="external-link">
          <h2>External link</h2>
          <p>
            I'm ma miss you when you leave but you can still checkout some more
            of my projects... Spoiler alert! JavaScript is involved.
          </p>
          <p>
            Find more stuff at
            <a href="https://developerdavis.netlify.app" target="_blank">
              my projects</a
            >
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="comments" id="comments">
          <h2>Leave a comment</h2>
          <p>
            You can let others know about what you think of my work and advise
            on where I could have done better.
          </p>

          <div class="comments-available">
            <% if(comments){ %> <% comments.forEach(comment => { %>
            <div class="comment">
              <h3><%= comment.commenterName %></h3>
              <p><%= comment.commentBody %></p>
            </div>
            <% }) %> <% } %>
          </div>
          <form action="/add-comment" method="post">
            <input
              name="commenterName"
              type="text"
              id="name"
              placeholder="Your name"
              required
            />
            <textarea
              name="commentBody"
              id="comment"
              cols="30"
              rows="10"
              placeholder="Write your comment here"
              required
            ></textarea>
            <input type="submit" value="Add comment" />
          </form>
        </div>

        <div class="contacts" id="contacts">
          <h2>Contact me</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions or want to get in touch with me, feel free
            to contact me at
          </p>
          <div class="handles">
            <div class="handle">
              <span>Tell</span>
              <a href="Tel:+256753460522">+256 753 460522</a>
            </div>
            <div class="handle">
              <span>Whatsapp</span>
              <a href="https://wa.me/+256753460522"> +256 753 460522</a>
            </div>
            <div class="handle">
              <span>Email</span>
              <a href="mailto:kimdhev@gmail.com"> kimdhev@gmail.com</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>
      <footer>
        <p class="copyright">&copy; Davis 2024</p>
        <div class="social">
          <a href="Tel:+256753460522"
            ><img src="images/dialer.png" alt="tel" /></a
          ><a href="https://wa.me/+256753460522"
